{"tid":1502743,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非］行動進化， 手機喇叭","createTime":"2019-08-24T17:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:28:50.000Z","uid":233019,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1bfc46fb2933a0d9369a26ca2677cd6adfbd152b","tid":1502743,"uid":233019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:16:01.000Z","msg":"如果細過讀過聖經， 都應該聽過歌利亞城牆的故事。<br />\n到第七日， 一齊吹號角， 產生共鳴， 推倒城牆。<br />\n<br />\n我地與其同班差佬鬧交， 不如用一個洗腦方法對佢地。<br />\n不停咁講同一樣野， 或者口號。<br />\n洗佢地腦， 或者聽都癲。<br />\n<br />\n我地用自己既手機， 一齊播同一句口號。<br />\n聽到佢煩， 聽到佢入腦， 聽到佢信我地， 聽到佢懷疑自己。<br />\n<br />\n一黎又唔駛叫到口都軟， 二黎又可以叫到好齊。<br />\n<br />\n方法好簡單：搵人錄完音， 手機一齊播， 記住要不停重播。<br />\n<br />\n可能<br />\n男聲： 警察OT, 警嫂3p<br />\n女聲： 警察， 強姦犯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa